  3. gpt-5.4            Strong model for everyday coding.
  4. gpt-5.4-mini       Small, fast, and cost-efficient model for simpler
                        coding tasks.
  5. gpt-5.3-codex      Coding-optimized model.
› 6. gpt-5.2 (current)  Optimized for professional work and long-running
